<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 03:02:43 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a5ee14f87954</link><description>&lt;p&gt;帕特拉&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Cachorro dorme com almofada " height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/sergio/6a5ee14f87954.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://sergio.some.pics"&gt;@sergio&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 03:02:43 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Pascal语录依旧深刻</title><link>https://some.pics/6a5ed58faceb6</link><description>&lt;p&gt;我很喜欢《动物森友会：口袋露营》里的引用小工具仍然活跃。不管是谁写了帕斯卡的这些语录，都确实在其中玩得很尽兴。其中不少内容其实还挺有见地的！&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Screenshot of the quote widget from Animal Crossing Pocket Camp with Pascal’s face in lower left corner and a quote: “They say the early bird gets the worm, but those evening birds seem to be doing just fine, maaan.” " height="590" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/jezlyn/6a5ed58faceb6.jpg" width="1187"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://jezlyn.some.pics"&gt;@jezlyn&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 02:12:34 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a5e8d22f0846</link><description>&lt;p&gt;天空中的文字，纽约（2012）&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Words in the sky, New York (2012)" height="2232" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/hiddenflair/6a5e8d22f0846.jpg" width="3968"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://hiddenflair.some.pics"&gt;@hiddenflair&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 21:03:35 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a5e8bcf0cc4c</link><description>&lt;p&gt;海滩日&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A large Magikarp plushie wearing a multicolored lei sits in the sand at a rocky beach on a cloudy day." height="3000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/plaster/6a5e8bcf0cc4c.jpg" width="4000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://plaster.some.pics"&gt;@plaster&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 20:57:54 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>路边绿</title><link>https://some.pics/6a5e558b65dac</link><description>&lt;p&gt;路边绿化&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A plant featuring fragile twigs and small yellow blossoms above street stones. Dreamlike blur effect applied." height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a5e558b65dac.jpg" width="1126"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 17:06:22 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>